{"tid":1250431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘停車場冇秘道","createTime":"2019-06-22T05:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T05:43:31.000Z","uid":148709,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b9f16930da653536265a74be005d273ef225a935","tid":1250431,"uid":148709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:32:31.000Z","msg":"發夢係隻工蟻同探路，想講金鐘停車場。<br />\n<br />\n立法會有兩條2個秘道通往特首辦<br />\n警總都有秘道機會好大<br />\n金鐘停車場太近警總，本身有後門入出<br />\n已check兩層停車場加入面風機房，冇任何暗門<br />\n有唔少人覺得可疑去check<br />\n加上唔符合暗門另外一邊最好係可控區域<br />\n基本上已經確定冇秘道<br />\n<br />\n其他可能地點： <br />\n特首辦<br />\n立法會<br />\n政總<br />\n金鐘站<br />\n軍營<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9kqbdu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9kqbdu.png&h=688013bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3013ea54b8b5cb3f536fc9e502de265e8a9b7f6f","tid":1250431,"uid":242630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:34:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c02471fe3b1fd077a701cffdfe60ecc8323207d","tid":1250431,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"勁"}]}